### Component Libraries

#### 1. Shadcn UI (Primary Component Library)

**Project Standard:** Use Shadcn UI for all new components and UI updates.

**Documentation Sources:**
- **Official Registry:** https://ui.shadcn.com
- **Component Docs:** https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/[component-name]
- **MCP Server:** Use `mcp_presenter-agent-ui-shadcn_*` tools to explore and view components
- **GitHub:** https://github.com/shadcn-ui/ui

**Access Methods:**
```bash
# Via CLI
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add [component-name]

# Via MCP Tools (Recommended)
# Use mcp_presenter-agent-ui-shadcn_* tools for exploration
```

**Key Guidelines:**
- ✅ Use Shadcn components for consistency
- ✅ Follow component patterns from examples
- ✅ Customize via className, not by modifying source
- ✅ Use `size="sm"` for buttons in application context
- ✅ Use `h-9` for inputs
- ❌ Never modify Shadcn component source files directly
- ❌ Never use `Loader2` (use `Spinner` from `@shadcn/spinner` instead)

**Available Components:** 438+ components including:
- Layout: Card, Separator, Sidebar, Breadcrumb, Tabs
- Forms: Input, Label, Textarea, Select, Checkbox, Radio, Switch, Accordion
- Feedback: Alert, Badge, Spinner, Skeleton, Progress, Toast
- Data: Table, Pagination, Empty, Avatar
- Overlays: Dialog, Drawer, Sheet, Dropdown Menu, Popover, Tooltip
- Advanced: Command, Calendar, Chart, Carousel, Form

**See UI_UX_GUIDE.md Part III for complete component reference.**

